Package: redisProgress
Type: Package
Title: Follow task progression using Redis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Clément TURBELIN
Maintainer: Clément TURBELIN <clement.turbelin@upmc.fr>
Description: Follow tasks progression in a distributed context, using a Redis instance to exchange data about running tasks. Redis is not used as a job queue here (unlike doRedis package), only as a mean to share data about tasks progression.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: 
    methods
Suggests: 
    rredis,
    RCppRedis,
    redux,
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
